hands_on_practices.solution:
1.  在无质量共线极限下，自旋平均的顶点振幅平方为
$$|{\cal M}|^2 \;=\; 4e^2\,\frac{1+z^2}{1-z}\,\frac{k_T^2}{(k_T^2)^2}
\;=\;4e^2\,\frac{1+z^2}{1-z}\,\frac{1}{k_T^2}\,. $$

2.  微分分裂概率为
$$dP \;=\;\frac{1}{2k^+}|{\cal M}|^2\,d{\rm PS}_{\rm coll}
\;\propto\;\frac{\alpha}{2\pi}\,\frac{dk_T^2}{k_T^2}\,dz\;
P_{ee}(z)\,. $$

3.  匹配系数可得
$$P_{ee}(z)\;=\;\frac{1+z^2}{1-z}\,. $$
